      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "# Simple Citations 1.6.1\n\n## Bug Fixes\n\n### BetterBibTeX JSON: year parsing for MM/YYYY date format\n- Fixed an issue where dates in `MM/YYYY` format (e.g. `\"07/2019\"`) were parsed as the month number instead of the year.\n- The `year` property is now correctly extracted from all common date formats found in BetterBibTeX JSON exports: `YYYY`, `YYYY-MM`, `YYYY-MM-DD`, `YYYY/MM/DD`, and `MM/YYYY`.\n",
      "downloadCount": 184,
