      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "# Simple Citations 1.5.1\n\n## Bug Fixes\n\n### Zotero select URL for group libraries\n- Fixed incorrect Zotero select URL generation for items in group libraries.\n- Previously, group library items used the personal library URL format (`zotero://select/items/@key`), which did not open the correct item in Zotero.\n- Now correctly generates `zotero://select/groups/{groupId}/items/@key` when the item belongs to a group library.\n\n## Contributors\n\n- [@haiqiang-zhang](https://github.com/haiqiang-zhang) — [#8](https://github.com/masaki39/simple-citations/pull/8)\n",
